subSubSection.paragraph:
Description ( holotype values refer to
P. promelas
). Meristics: precaudal vertebrae 16–17, 0–1 last vertebrae without ribs; pectoral-fin rays 18 (17–18); D/V = 5–6; D/A = 24–29; V/A = 18–19; long gill rakers on first gill arch 18 (15–18). Gill rakers in paralectotype (USNM 125002) on lower first gill arch with five plate like rakers, followed by a series of 15 long rakers. The lower 10 of those intercept by broad plate shaped rakers, placed between the long rakers. Upper gill raker with a series of four semi long rakers and five plate like rakers intercepted.

